Introduction:
---------------------------------
FaabBB is an open-source website management system and development framework written in PHP.
You can use it as Community or CMS as well for your PHP application. 

FaabBB has support for several SQL servers including MySQL and Microsoft SQL. FaabBB has a
SQL system with Logic, a powerful content management system and plenty plugins.

---------------------------------
Using FaabBB
---------------------------------

Requirements:
	* PHP 5.3+
	* A SQL Server. (MySQL)
	* Common sense.
	
Extract the download and navigate to the following url:
	http://yourwebsite.com/folderinstalled/install.php
Localhost:
	http://localhost/folderinstalled/install.php

FaabBB is developed and tested using Eclipse on a Ubuntu system, so you should be able to import
this project in Eclipse which should detect the project layout
automatically.

